            <p>Бронзовыя медали на <name type="event" ref="events.xml#crime02">соединение <placeName ref="place.xml#cri01">Крыма</placeName></name> и на <name type="event" ref="events.xml#monum01">монумент <persName ref="people.xml#pet01">Петра перваго</persName></name>, да золотая медаль о <name type="event" ref="events.xml#crime02">соединении <placeName ref="place.xml#cri01">Крыма</placeName></name>, да золотая четыре-угольная, при мире данная солдатам.
                <!--I assume that it must be the medal for the treaty of Kuchuk Kainardzhi, but in all descriptions it is described as a silver medal and Catherine writes about a golden one--> 
            </p>
